
Project setup for include dependencies for Tomcat

You need to add the "Maven Dependency" in the Deployment Assembly

	1.right click on your project and choose properties.
	2.click on Deployment Assembly.
	3.click add
	4.click on "Java Build Path Entries"
	5.select Maven Dependencies"
	6.click Finish.
	7.Rebuild and deploy again

Note: This is also applicable for non maven project.




Start up the application :
	1. Build and Run the application using Maven Build with   clean install 
	2. Run As -> Run on server
	
	
	
Url

	http://localhost:8080/SpringMVCCRUDSimple/
  	
  	
  	
   
   
   